Dirty Halong Bay
Unpleasant experience - the sea was filthy with rubbish everywhere as the ship sails, dock and when we went for kayaking. It is very sad to see the UNESCO site was not preserved and well-maintained by the government. I did not like my cruise I have chosen and would not return to Halong Bay as it was not a pretty sight to see the rubbish on the sea.
Written February 22, 2024
